|| Image Changer App

A simple web project that allows users to change images by clicking buttons. This is a beginner-friendly JavaScript-based project, ideal for learning DOM manipulation and event handling.

||🔥 Features

- Change images with the click of a button  
- Simple and clean UI  
- HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript  
- Beginner-friendly project  

|| 🚀 Live Demo

|| 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML  
- CSS  
- JavaScript  

