|| ⚙️ How to Run

1. Clone this repository  
   `git clone https://github.com/farhanbaber/image-changer.git`

2. Open the folder  
   `cd image-changer`

3. Open `index.html` in any browser.

|| 💡 How It Works

Each button is linked to a JavaScript function that changes the `src` attribute of the image element.

Example:

```javascript
function changeImage(imagePath) {
  document.getElementById('mainImage').src = imagePath;
}
```

